  <brief_title>Comparison of Single and Repeated Dose of Vaginal Misoprostol for the Treatment of Early Pregnancy Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Single and Repeated Dose of Vaginal Misoprostol for the Treatment of Early Pregnancy Failure - a Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
